T1  - Impact of Electronic Data Interchange Technology on JIT Shipments
AU  - Srinivasan, Kannan
AU  - Kekre, Sundar
AU  - Mukhopadhyay, Tridas
Y1  - 1994/10/01
PY  - 1994
DA  - 1994/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.40.10.1291
